1951;;Old Mother Riley's Jungle Treasure;;British;;Maclean Rogers;;Arthur Lucan, Kitty McShane;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_Mother_Riley%27s_Jungle_Treasure;;Mother Riley, working in an antique shop with daughter Kitty, uncovers a secret treasure map hidden in the headboard of an antique bed. With the help of the ghost of the pirate Captain Morgan, mother and daughter head for a remote tropical island in the South Seas, and begin their hunt for buried treasure. Not only do they find the fortune, but Mother Riley ends up celebrated by natives as a tribal queen.[3][4][5]